      <div class="page-header__byline"><img src="/images/damion.jpg" alt="Damien Mitchell" width="32" height="32" class="byline-avatar" /><span>By <a href="/about-us/" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: none;">Damien Mitchell</a>, USHPA Advanced Instructor</span></div>
    </div>
